Description:
Close all standard streams, resetting seekable stdin if needed, and exiting with a diagnostic on error.

Files:
lib/closein.h
lib/closein.c
m4/closein.m4

Depends-on:
closeout
freadahead
fflush
stdbool

configure.ac:
gl_CLOSEIN

Makefile.am:
lib_SOURCES += closein.c

Include:
"closein.h"

